headline: Why Cencora (COR) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of healthcare distributor Cencora (NYSE:COR) jumped 4.5% in the afternoon session after peer company McKesson raised its long-term earnings growth outlook, boosting investor sentiment across the pharmaceutical distribution sector.
